{
  "stem": "3721.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anyway, we were going around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we saved-- I believe we saved quite a few people this way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we put them into the safe houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That's the time when, if you remember, Wallenberg opened up the safe houses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "For the Swedish safe houses, I had 40, 50 certificates in the place that I slept.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Of course, not with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Or I would-- they would tell me, like I told you before, is that they took away such-and-such people by such-and-such a name, and the certificates would be made out to their name.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I would go, as a Hungarian officer, go into where they kept them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was a brick factory they kept these people to be shipped, either to Auschwitz or, or to-- actually, they walked them to-- towards Vienna.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I would go and take them out with these Schutz-Passes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were already [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] made for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I, I, I remember meeting Wallenberg himself-- on a few occasions, actually.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we used these Schutz-Passes for quite-- a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But then, I was called in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I was told that I have to pick up something in, in, in, I believe, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- but I should not go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They made me brand new papers then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I should go as a Hungarian refugee, who is running away from the area in my hometown.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And again, they gave me genuine birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They also gave me a certificate then that I was medically circumcised, although that you don't show unless they ask-- they, they take your pants down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Anyway, we went to this place by the name Kecskemet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Bilitzer instructed us that when we get to [NON-ENGLISH], to go to the Jewish community, and just a certain password.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
